items.title: Ancient Egyptian mummies still smell nice, study finds
items.description: Rsearchers find nine mummies they examined all smelled "woody", "spicy" and "sweet".

items.title: Infant mortality rises in US states with abortion bans, study finds
items.description: Some states restrict access for women following the overturning of Roe v Wade.

items.title: Hamas releases names of hostages due for release on Saturday
items.description: They are set to be released in exchange for Palestinian prisoners held in Israel.

items.title: Resignations after DOJ tells prosecutors to drop NY mayor case
items.description: Top New York attorney Danielle Sassoon is among several prosecutors to quit over an order to drop a corruption case against Eric Adams.

items.title: Chernobyl radiation shield hit by Russian drone, Ukraine says
items.description: There has been no increase in radiation levels at the plant, Ukraine's president says.
